# Pyreqwest_impersonate

The fastest python HTTP client that can impersonate web browsers.</br>
Provides precompiled wheels: üêß`linux|musllinux` (*amd64*, *aarch64*), ü™ü`windows` (*amd64*); üçè`macos` (*amd64*, *aarch64*).

